Class JsonEncoding

Enumeration that defines legal encodings that can be used for JSON content, based on list of allowed encodings from JSON specification.

Limitation: currently only UTF-8 encoding is supported.

@since 1.3 @author Yaniv InbarInbar @deprecated (scheduled to be removed in 1.11)

Class JsonParser

Abstract low-level JSON parser.

Implementation has no fields and therefore thread-safe, but sub-classes are not necessarily thread-safe.

Backwards incompatibility warning: 1.9 introduced .getUnsignedIntegerValue andand .getUnsignedLongValue to this abstract class.

@since 1.3 @author Yaniv Inbar
